<h1 style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 22px; color: #333;">Account Deleted</h1>

<p style="font-size: 15px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px;">
  Hi <%= @user.name %>, your Care account has been deleted and all associated data has been removed.
</p>

<div style="background-color: #ffebee; border-left: 4px solid #e53935; padding: 14px 18px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 0 0 20px;">
  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5;">
    If you didn't request this, please contact us immediately at
    <a href="mailto:<%= support_email %>" style="color: #e53935; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;"><%= support_email %></a>
  </p>
</div>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #999; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
  We're sorry to see you go. You're always welcome back.
</p>
